description:
As a merchant
  I turn ON paypal spb checkout, mini fast checkout
  still can use add to cart checkout order
name: Fast-Checkout Add to cart tax setting and credit - Login at fast checkout page

elements.name: Fast-Checkout Add to cart tax setting and credit - Login at fast checkout page

steps.name: I am on Admin Login Page
I fill correct account email to email field
I fill correct account password to password field
I click on login button
I should see successful login
I check intercom message notification frame and click clear intercom message button
I check intercom message notification frame and click intercom message close button
I check new feature alert notification frame and click new feature alert close button
I check and click exclude products panel close button
I check and click no thanks button
I am on Customer List Page
I input email to search field
I should see view button
I click view button for the same order of customer row included 'testuser@shoplineapp.com'
I should be redirected to Customer Detail Page
I click on assign credits button
I should see popover
I fill "20" to amount of credit field
I click on never expires button
I fill "Testing amount of credits" to reason field
I click on credit save button
I should see row of credit list
I am on Promotion Create Page
I fill "(dirty data)invalid payment/delivery coupon" to name field
I fill "20" to promotion value field
I should see countinue to button
I click on countinue to button
I click on 2nd countinue to button
I click on apply method checkbox included 'codes'
I should see coupon code field
I fill "invalidCoupon" to coupon code field
I click on 3rd countinue to button
I check delivery options checkbox and click all of them
I click on payment options checkbox included 'Custom'
